What happens to user input during the reload?

If follow our current design, then AI may drawing the UI and take some minutes.
It may considered some state at some time when AI read. ya, it may be stale.
Even through, just before the deploy, client side can send new state to sync file state,
but AI is already finished the updating logic, it didnt see any latest changes, so it will not know to cater the recent new states.
